snippet.title: Handball 17 - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Take your favourite teams onto the court and play as the biggest stars in the world of handball! 
The Handball 17 season begins in October 2016 on PC, PlayStation®4, PlayStation®3 and Xbox One.
Learn more: http://handball-thegame.com/
